<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SpinalDecompression.com | Something New is Coming</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-primary: #0c4c54;
            --color-bg-dark: #050228;
            --color-action: #ff6b6b;
            --color-text-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            --color-text-muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--color-bg-dark);
            background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, #024856 0%, #050228 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            line-height: 1.2;
            padding-bottom: 0.1em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        p {
            font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.25rem);
            color: var(--color-text-light);
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
            border-radius: 99px;
            color: var(--color-action);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: var(--color-action);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--color-action);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--color-text-muted);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: var(--color-action);
            border-color: var(--color-action);
        }

        /* Background pattern */
        .waves {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0.15;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <svg class="waves" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 120" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <g fill="none" stroke="#024856" stroke-width="2" stroke-opacity="0.5">
            <path d="M-500 75c0 0 125-30 250-30S0 75 0 75s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30s125-30 250-30s250 30 250 30s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30"/>
            <path d="M-500 45c0 0 125-30 250-30S0 45 0 45s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30s125-30 250-30s250 30 250 30s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30"/>
            <path d="M-500 105c0 0 125-30 250-30S0 105 0 105s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30s125-30 250-30s250 30 250 30s125 30 250 30s250-30 250-30"/>
        </g>
    </svg>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://imagedelivery.net/ye6TBwd9tSy8dGYL2VHjgg/cad90d3a-cd81-431a-ea37-9ce097649e00/public" alt="Spinal Decompression Logo" class="logo">
        
        <div class="status-badge">
            <span class="status-dot"></span>
            System Upload in Progress
        </div>

        <h1>Something New is Coming</h1>
        
        <p>
            We're currently upgrading the SpinalDecompression.com platform to provide a better experience for our patients and providers. Check back soon for our new look.
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        Are you a Practice? <a href="https://portal.spinaldecompression.com">Access Provider Portal</a>
        <br><br>
        &copy; 2026 SpinalDecompression.com. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

